  "text": "Several methods lift 2D detections efficiently to 3D by means of triangulation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . More closely related to our work, [CITATION_5] proposes to back-propagate through an SVDbased differentiable triangulation layer by lifting 2D detections to 3D keypoints. Unlike our approach, these methods do not perform any explicit reasoning about multi-view inputs and therefore struggle with large self-occlusions.",
